Package: binancer
Type: Package
Title: Retrieve Cryptocurrency Data from Binance
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Beniamino", "Sartini", email = "beniaminosartini@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for retrieving cryptocurrency market data from the
    Binance REST API, Binance Vision public data archive, and Binance WebSocket
    streams. It includes helpers for price tickers, order books, trades,
    candlestick data, futures statistics, and authenticated account or order
    endpoints when user-supplied credentials are available.
